<div class="live-post__wrapper-body-article">
<h3 class="live-post__title">Cases soar in the Netherlands</h3>
<div class="articleBodyText section">
<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">T</span>he number of confirmed coronavirus infections in the Netherlands jumped by a record of more than 5,800 in 24 hours, data released by health authorities showed.</p>
<p>The rapid rise is putting pressure on authorities to impose new restrictions in the country, which has one of the highest per capita infection rates in the world.</p>
</div>
