<h3 class="live-post__title">EU seals vaccine supply deal with Johnson &amp; Johnson</h3>
<div class="articleBodyText section">
<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">T</span>he European Commission said on Thursday it had sealed a supply deal with Johnson &amp; Johnson for the supply of its potential Covid-19 vaccine for up to 400 million people.</p>
<p>This is the third advance purchase contract signed by the EU with makers of Covid-19 vaccines after deals with AstraZeneca and Sanofi. </p>
