<div class="live-post__wrapper-body-article">
<h3 class="live-post__title">Majority of passengers let off for not wearing face mask</h3>
<div class="articleBodyText section">
<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">T</span>ransport for London (TfL) has defended its policy of not fining the vast majority of passengers caught without a face covering.</p>
<p>The organisation insisted that offenders who are let off with a warning are likely to follow the rules on their next journey.</p>
<p>It has been mandatory to wear a face covering on public transport in England since June 15, in a bid to tackle the spread of coronavirus.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
