<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">T</span>fL and British Transport Police (BTP) conducted a joint enforcement operation at King's Cross St Pancras Tube station on Thursday.</p>
<p>Passengers stopped for not wearing a face covering did not face further action if they had one with them and put it on.</p>
