<a href="#update-20201008-1043"><time class="live-post__wrapper-body-timestamp-full" datetime="2020-10-08T10:43:00.319+01:00">10:43AM</time></a>
<div class="live-post__wrapper-body-article">
<h3 class="live-post__title">Fears of  &#39;one last party before Christmas&#39;</h3>
<div class="articleBodyText section">
<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">L</span>ocal leaders have warned that people will see this weekend as &quot;their last chance before Christmas&quot; to have a party, as they attack the Government for dragging its heels on new restrictions in England. </p>
<p>David Mellen, leader of Nottingham City Council, told Radio 4's Today programme that even though the city had &quot;very high numbers&quot; they now had to &quot;wait until next week for the Government to bring in what we expect to be new restrictions&quot;. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="articleBodyImage section">
<div class="article-body-image component " itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" data-frz-ancestor>
