<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">A</span>s well as that allowing the virus extra time to spread, that could mean &quot;people think 'this is our last chance before Christmas'  and go have a party,&quot; Mr Mellen said. &quot;We can't have that.&quot;</p>
<p>Nottingham looks set to be the latest area to face new restrictions following a surge in infections.</p>
