<h3 class="live-post__title">Trump thankful for Johnson&#39;s support</h3>
<div class="articleBodyText section">
<div class="article-body-text component  ">
<div class="component-content">
<p><span class="m_first-letter m_first-letter--flagged">D</span>onald Trump reveals that he has spoken on the phone with Prime Minister Boris Johnson, who also fell ill from Covid-19 earlier this year.</p>
</div>
