<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2020/10/07/prime-minister-may-shut-pubs-despite-mounting-labour-opposition/">Boris Johnson is considering plans to close pubs and restaurants</a> within days amid mounting opposition from Sir Keir Starmer to the Government’s lockdown strategy.</li>
<li>Blanket social distancing and the closure of schools may have <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/10/07/herd-immunity-could-have-saved-lives-lockdown-study-suggests/">cost more lives than if herd immunity had been allowed</a> to build slowly in the community, a study suggests.</li>
