<li><a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/10/07/official-sparks-ire-claims-nhs-wasopen-business-everyone-needed/">A top health official has sparked anger</a> after claiming the NHS has been “open for business for everyone who needed it” during the pandemic.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/10/07/specialist-long-covid-clinics-set-says-boss-nhs-england/">Long-Covid centres are to be established by the NHS </a>to care for people suffering long-term effects of the virus.</li>
